Extension Features:

1. Switch up your Billie Eilish wallpaper with every new tab opened.
2. Set a random Billie Eilish background or select your favorite from the wallpaper panel.
3. Integrated Google search bar.
4. Direct links to your email and social media platforms.
5. Automatic display of the current date and time.
6. Note-taking feature for jotting down tasks.
7. Convenient access to frequently visited websites.
8. Shortcut to your bookmarked pages.
9. Add sites to your Shortcut panel for faster navigation.
10. Instant access to Google applications.
11. Explore additional themes easily.
12. Share content seamlessly on social media.
13. Download wallpapers directly from the tab.
14. One-click access to online gaming.
15. Activate dynamic animations like snow, rain, falling leaves, or fireworks in your Billie Eilish tab.
